{"tid":1994490,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我勸你哋班人唔好對個選舉咁老定","createTime":"2020-04-29T13:32:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-30T16:31:01.000Z","uid":280730,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"632fc5bdd3ae01ec8c4fe3f80295d2f9de382800","tid":1994490,"uid":280730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T13:32:52.000Z","msg":"香港人就最貪錢同小便宜嘅<br />\n7月俾佢攞咗政府果1萬蚊 你就應該會見到民意又反彈<br />\n對家又嚇佢哋攬炒無飯開 應該真係帶動到唔少諗嘢簡單淨係理錢嘅中立撚投佢 <br />\n依家又好似抗疫成功咁 啲人對政府嘅好感值又會升<br />\n<br />\n我自己覺得黃嘅鐵票已經係度 嚟緊應該係要響經濟民生方面吸引啲中間派 繼續煲番起建制支持超支大白象果啲嘢 話自己當選之後會極力還富於民之類果啲 <br />\n甚至話投建制=繼續攬炒 自己就可以&ldquo;制止攬炒&rdquo; 我相信黃嘅都會理解"},{"pid":"0fc7e48a96890efe6b498cd5df1fd463f6523ca2","tid":1994490,"uid":133086,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T13:35:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sUPbGv1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsUPbGv1.png&h=28f32eaa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3d9f0e8e5d4edd5fa2e7252c3fb81848311e492a","tid":1994490,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T13:37:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9859f8dc14320cb076e0b696af733af81e6ffac2","tid":1994490,"uid":280730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0fc7e48a96890efe6b498cd5df1fd463f6523ca2","tid":1994490,"uid":133086,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T13:35:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sUPbGv1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsUPbGv1.png&h=28f32eaa&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T13:37:49.000Z","msg":"啱啊 其實藍絲真係比我哋想像中多 加埋對家嘅配票機器 真係唔係咁穩陣 <br />\n我哋為咗啲票真係要乜都做得出"},{"pid":"fde60ff39142eed804d24e9f201e433c3a0a8007","tid":1994490,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T13:38:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/n